data.description: Move right into this renovated 3-bedroom ranch. All the hard work has been done for you!   Updates include all new Flooring, new Paint throughout, Custom white shaker Kitchen cabinets, Granite countertops with custom tile backsplash and all new Stainless Steel Appliances are included!    Double vanity with storage, new shower enclosure.  Lots of storage in hall & closets and Full Basement with Laundry & 1/4 bath.  Immediate showings and quick closing are available. Seller is related to agent.
